Segues

What is a segue
movement from on veiw controler to another.
What is a segue identifier?
what the segue called in the program
How do you create segue from a button?
click and clr drag the button between viewcontrollers 
How do you create from a view controller without a button?
click the first veiw controller then clr drag over to the next one
What is the method to perfrom a segue called and what argument does it take?
perform segue
What method is called immediatly before a segue is performed?
perpare for segue
How do you assign a new view controller class?
class idenifier in the left tab on the storyborad file
How do you pass data between two view controllers? (this will need a few sentances to explain)
you use the prepare to segue func and then place the data you want ot pass through within the {}
You dont link a segue "backwards", why?
becuase it will just layer the views up and will eventually crash the phone.
should use dismiss() or the navigation bar.
